## Progressive Disclosure

**SKILL.md / Agent / Command Size:**
- Target: ≤200 lines for main file
- Rationale: Claude processes smaller files faster, context efficiency

**Structure:**
```
.claude/skills/skill-name/
├── SKILL.md                # Main file (≤200 lines)
├── README.md               # User-facing documentation
├── references/             # Detailed documentation
│   ├── patterns.md         # Design patterns
│   ├── examples.md         # Extended examples
│   └── edge-cases.md       # Edge case handling
└── templates/              # Code templates (if applicable)
```

**References/ Guidelines:**
- Each document ≤600 lines (keeps manageable)
- Link from SKILL.md using relative links
- Provide depth without bloating main file

