## YAML Frontmatter Validation

### Skills Frontmatter
```yaml
---
name: skill-name
type: Discipline | Technique | Pattern | Reference
auto_invoke: true | false
cso_score: 0.73  # Calculated score
created: 2025-11-10
---
```

**Required Fields:** name, type, auto_invoke, cso_score

### Agents Frontmatter
```yaml
---
name: agent-name
tool_tier: read_only | read_web | full_access
description: Brief description of agent purpose
created: 2025-11-10
---
```

**Required Fields:** name, tool_tier, description

**Tool Tiers:**
- `read_only`: Read, Glob, Grep, WebFetch only
- `read_web`: read_only + WebSearch
- `full_access`: All tools including Write, Edit, Bash

### Commands Frontmatter
```yaml
---
name: command-name
workflow_type: RPIV | Human Approval | Reflection | Validation | Batch | Routing | ETL | Orchestration | Reporting
description: Brief description of command purpose
created: 2025-11-10
---
```

**Required Fields:** name, workflow_type, description

