## Naming Conventions

**Files:**
- Skills: `skill-name/SKILL.md` (kebab-case)
- Agents: `agent-name.md` (kebab-case)
- Commands: `command-name.md` (kebab-case)
- Templates: `template-name.template` (kebab-case + .template extension)

**Directories:**
```
.claude/
├── skills/
│   └── skill-name/                 # kebab-case
├── agents/
│   ├── validators/                 # group by function
│   │   └── agent-name.md           # kebab-case
│   └── generators/
│       └── agent-name.md
├── commands/
│   ├── development-workflows/      # group by context (Q7 decision)
│   │   └── command-name.md         # kebab-case
│   └── fpa-workflows/
│       └── command-name.md
```

