## Tool Tier Enforcement

**Read-Only Agents (Validators):**
- Use when: Validation, review, checking (no modifications)
- Can use: Read, Glob, Grep, WebFetch
- Cannot use: Write, Edit, Bash, NotebookEdit
- Examples: @databricks-validator, @report-formatter

**Full Access Agents (Generators):**
- Use when: Code generation, file creation, script execution
- Can use: All tools including Write, Edit, Bash
- Requires: Careful validation before execution
- Examples: @script-generator, @test-generator

**Rationale:** Validators should not accidentally modify files (read-only prevents errors)

