## Integration Testing

**Test Skill Auto-Invoke:**
```bash
# Verify trigger phrases work
echo "create hook" | grep -q "hook-factory"  # Should match

# Verify CSO scoring
python scripts/validation/cso-scorer.py .claude/skills/skill-name/SKILL.md
```

**Test Agent Tool Tier:**
```bash
# Verify read-only agent cannot Write
# (Manual test: Try using Write tool in read-only agent, expect error)
```

**Test Command Workflow:**
```bash
# Verify command invocation
/command-name arg1 arg2
# Check expected behavior
```

